======================================================================
PART 1: PERM(A) vs DET(A) FOR TOURNAMENT ADJACENCY
======================================================================

n=3 (m=3, 2^m=8):
  perm=-det: 2/8 (25.0%)
  perm=det: 6/8 (75.0%)

  By H value:
    H=  1: {(0, 0): 6}
    H=  3: {(-1, 1): 2}

  perm = (-1)^{m} det: 8/8 (sign_factor=-1)
  perm² = det²: 8/8

n=4 (m=6, 2^m=64):
  perm=-det: 24/64 (37.5%)
  perm=det: 40/64 (62.5%)

  By H value:
    H=  1: {(0, 0): 24}
    H=  3: {(0, 0): 16}
    H=  5: {(1, -1): 24}

  perm = (-1)^{m} det: 40/64 (sign_factor=1)
  perm² = det²: 64/64

n=5 (m=10, 2^m=1024):
  perm=-det: 544/1024 (53.1%)
  perm=det: 480/1024 (46.9%)

  By H value:
    H=  1: {(0, 0): 120}
    H=  3: {(0, 0): 120}
    H=  5: {(0, 0): 240}
    H=  9: {(-1, 1): 240}
    H= 11: {(-1, 1): 120}
    H= 13: {(-2, 2): 120}
    H= 15: {(-3, 3): 40, (-2, 2): 24}

  perm = (-1)^{m} det: 480/1024 (sign_factor=1)
  perm² = det²: 1024/1024

n=6 (m=15, 2^m=32768):
  other(2,0): 720/32768 (2.2%)
  other(3,-1): 2160/32768 (6.6%)
  other(4,-2): 4800/32768 (14.6%)
  other(5,-1): 720/32768 (2.2%)
  other(5,-3): 1440/32768 (4.4%)
  other(6,-2): 2880/32768 (8.8%)
  other(6,-4): 1680/32768 (5.1%)
  other(7,-3): 720/32768 (2.2%)
  other(9,-1): 240/32768 (0.7%)
  perm=-det: 6960/32768 (21.2%)
  perm=det: 10448/32768 (31.9%)

  By H value:
    H=  1: {(0, 0): 720}
    H=  3: {(0, 0): 960}
    H=  5: {(0, 0): 2160}
    H=  9: {(0, 0): 2880, (1, 1): 80}
    H= 11: {(0, 0): 1440}
    H= 13: {(0, 0): 1440}
    H= 15: {(0, 0): 768, (1, -1): 1440}
    H= 17: {(1, -1): 720, (2, 0): 720}
    H= 19: {(1, -1): 1440}
    H= 23: {(1, -1): 1440, (3, -1): 1440}
    H= 25: {(2, -2): 1440}
    H= 27: {(4, -2): 480}
    H= 29: {(3, -1): 720, (4, -2): 1440, (5, -1): 720}
    H= 31: {(4, -2): 1440}
    H= 33: {(3, -3): 480, (4, -2): 1440, (6, -2): 720}
    H= 37: {(5, -3): 1440, (6, -2): 1440, (7, -3): 720}
    H= 41: {(6, -2): 720}
    H= 43: {(6, -4): 1440}
    H= 45: {(6, -4): 240, (9, -1): 240}

  perm = (-1)^{m} det: 17328/32768 (sign_factor=-1)
  perm² = det²: 17408/32768

======================================================================
PART 2: PFAFFIAN OF SKEW-ADJACENCY S = A - A^T
======================================================================

n=4:
  Pfaffian distribution: {-3: 8, -1: 24, 1: 24, 3: 8}
  Pfaffian² distribution: {1: 48, 9: 16}
    H=1: Pf values = [-1, 1]
    H=3: Pf values = [-3, 3]
    H=5: Pf values = [-1, 1]

  |Pf| → H mapping:
    |Pf|=1: H = [1, 5]
    |Pf|=3: H = [3]

n=5:
  n odd: Pf = 0 always (det(S) = 0)

n=6:
  Pfaffian distribution: {-9: 640, -7: 1920, -5: 2304, -3: 3840, -1: 7680, 1: 7680, 3: 3840, 5: 2304, 7: 1920, 9: 640}
